accessibility.text: TikTok, YouTube, Facebook, WhatsApp, and Instagram comprise 86% of all social media use in Singapore.
Having a brand presence on these platforms is essential and can be done efficiently and effectively.
With a DAM system, content can be created once and posted to the desired platforms at the optimal times both maximizing impact and ad spend.
06. 2025 Marketing Strategy | Optimizing Platform impact & Reach
